
xcode will compress PNG images for iPad/iPhone optimization, so dont use PNG images with corona, unless you disable the PNG compression in the project build settings....

Only use PNG images for iOS libs / xcode resources (like load screens).

Use jpg files in bbp with corona....

- Kevin




